Ranger Help for: attune
=======================

SYNTAX:      attune <target>
USAGE:       Any terrain
SLOT COST:   NA
BASE SP:     43
SKILL TYPE:  religious

SUMMARY:
This skill allows a Ranger to attune to a target's elemental weakness
through a brief communion with Gaia. Once attuned, the Ranger's attacks
will exploit that weakness for increased damage. Attunement lasts for a
limited duration and can only be active on one target at a time. This is
a religious skill, requiring devotion to Gaia to use effectively.
